      The make file, Makegnu, will make an executable xflip.  The OpenMP
  option is enabled. This requires giving the correct path to the library libgomp. 
  If unavailable, the file can be compiled in single-processor form by 
  removing -fopenmp from the command line.

      It would be preferable if the file is executed in sub-directory
  Projects. 

      The size of the arrays is set by parameter statements in corgan_com_M.f.

      
